item.title: WTF is wrong? *pic to explain...*
item.dc:creator: @agent_nukks agent nukks
item.description:
@agent_nukks wrote:

If you used No-ip.Biz, then you will have to go back there, sign in. And then redo everything you have done, as your power outage turned off your DSL, so you now have a different IP. So go back to No-ip.Biz and redirect it by deleting your old one, and adding anew one. Hope it helps, Rep++ wanted plox.
